    <body><p><seg rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
一筆啓上仕候。<lb />
然ニ私十一月廿四日浪華出帆、同廿六夕上の関ニつき申候。<lb />
夫より今日下の関ニ参り其まゝ御とゞけ申上候。いづれ拝顔の上万々。<lb />
<seg rend="chitsuki_0" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 0em">謹言</seg>
<seg rend="jisage_2" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 2em">十二月三日<seg rend="chitsuki_0" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 0em">龍馬</seg></seg>
<seg rend="jisage_3" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 3em">聿大兄</seg>
<seg rend="jisage_6" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 6em">足下</seg>
<seg rend="jisage_2" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 2em">印藤様<seg rend="chitsuki_0" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 0em">直陰</seg></seg>
<lb />
